REMARKABLE RIVALRIES 
</P>
<P>
ON THE GRIDIRON: 
</P>
<P>
You want a happening? Here's a top 10 for football. 
</P>
<P>
1. Morse-Point Loma. 
</P>
<P>
2. Morse-Lincoln. 
</P>
<P>
3. Grossmont-Helix. 
</P>
<P>
4. Sweetwater-Chula Vista. 
</P>
<P>
5. Oceanside-El Camino. 
</P>
<P>
6. Vista-Rancho Buena Vista. 
</P>
<P>
7. St. Augustine-USDHS. 
</P>
<P>
8. San Marcos-San Pasqual. 
</P>
<P>
9. Poway-Mt. Carmel. 
</P>
<P>
10. Vista-Fallbrook. 
</P>
