</P>
<P>
2. Lincoln-Morse boys' basketball. 
</P>
<P>
3. Valhalla-Monte Vista wrestling. 
</P>
<P>
4. Poway-Mt. Carmel boys' basketball. 
</P>
<P>
5. Poway-Torrey Pines girls' volleyball. 
</P>
<P>
6. San Dieguito-Poway boys' volleyball. 
</P>
<P>
7. Mission Bay-USDHS baseball. 
</P>
<P>
8. La Jolla-University City boys' soccer. 
</P>
<P>
9. Madison-Patrick Henry softball. 
</P>
<P>
10. Torrey Pines-Bonita Vista girls' soccer. 
